{"source_id": "dm-zhao-yuanlong", "source_type": "dm_user", "message_id": "om_x100b57edd89f4880e2ba0ba42f80823", "chat_id": "ou_cfbb3a081027568887b6063c4f56d50a", "chat_type": "unknown", "sender_id": "ou_a36ba11e5fe850d9c828659dd55406da", "sender_name": "Chen Chao", "direction": "outgoing", "created_at": "2026-02-12 17:12", "content": "universal bscore的样本比较复杂，只按segment拆开来看psi维度还是有点粗，用的样本还得调整一下，ant/dormant segment外数的缺失率本来就会随时间一直上升，因为用的是缓存没有重新调，超过6个月universal bscore是不取的，ant segment 的话mpv11缺失就是没有调，cbi 7/8/9月的缺失率高应该是pipeline跑早了，但最新的缺失率是正常的。", "payload": {"content": "universal bscore的样本比较复杂，只按segment拆开来看psi维度还是有点粗，用的样本还得调整一下，ant/dormant segment外数的缺失率本来就会随时间一直上升，因为用的是缓存没有重新调，超过6个月universal bscore是不取的，ant segment 的话mpv11缺失就是没有调，cbi 7/8/9月的缺失率高应该是pipeline跑早了，但最新的缺失率是正常的。", "create_time": "2026-02-12 17:12", "deleted": false, "message_id": "om_x100b57edd89f4880e2ba0ba42f80823", "msg_type": "text", "sender": {"id": "ou_a36ba11e5fe850d9c828659dd55406da", "id_type": "open_id", "name": "Chen Chao", "sender_type": "user", "tenant_key": "1503d1037d07977c"}, "updated": false}}
{"source_id": "dm-zhao-yuanlong", "source_type": "dm_user", "message_id": "om_x100b57edd3f3cd34e2e49482e8345fe", "chat_id": "ou_cfbb3a081027568887b6063c4f56d50a", "chat_type": "unknown", "sender_id": "ou_a36ba11e5fe850d9c828659dd55406da", "sender_name": "Chen Chao", "direction": "outgoing", "created_at": "2026-02-12 17:13", "content": "总之有的segment外数不刷新是成本考虑，我们这边只能调整下监控的客群，dormant和ant太久的用户需要去掉，而且可能需要再按产品线拆开看psi", "payload": {"content": "总之有的segment外数不刷新是成本考虑，我们这边只能调整下监控的客群，dormant和ant太久的用户需要去掉，而且可能需要再按产品线拆开看psi", "create_time": "2026-02-12 17:13", "deleted": false, "message_id": "om_x100b57edd3f3cd34e2e49482e8345fe", "msg_type": "text", "sender": {"id": "ou_a36ba11e5fe850d9c828659dd55406da", "id_type": "open_id", "name": "Chen Chao", "sender_type": "user", "tenant_key": "1503d1037d07977c"}, "updated": false}}
